{"node_id":"demo-tax-act-2026:section:2","document_id":"demo-tax-act-2026","act_title":"Demo Tax Act 2026","node_type":"section","text":"2. Definition of Commissioner\n(1) In this Act, \"Commissioner\" means the Commissioner of Taxes appointed by the Board.\nProvided that the Board may assign jurisdiction to another tax authority.\nExplanation 1. Commissioner includes an officer authorized in writing by the Board.","normalized_text":"2. Definition of Commissioner\n(1) In this Act, \"Commissioner\" means the Commissioner of Taxes appointed by the Board.\nProvided that the Board may assign jurisdiction to another tax authority.\nExplanation 1. Commissioner includes an officer authorized in writing by the Board.","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"parent_id":"demo-tax-act-2026:chapter:chapter-i","child_ids":["demo-tax-act-2026:subsection:2-1"],"path_ids":["demo-tax-act-2026:act","demo-tax-act-2026:part:part-i","demo-tax-act-2026:chapter:chapter-i","demo-tax-act-2026:section:2"],"path_labels":["Demo Tax Act 2026","Part I","Chapter I","Section 2"],"label":"Section 2","title":"Definition of Commissioner","part_number":"I","part_title":"PRELIMINARY","chapter_number":"I","chapter_title":"GENERAL PROVISIONS","section_number":"2","subsection_number":null,"clause_number":null,"proviso_number":null,"explanation_number":null,"page_anchor_text":"2. Definition of Commissioner","cross_references":[],"metadata":{"node_id":"demo-tax-act-2026:section:2","document_id":"demo-tax-act-2026","act_title":"Demo Tax Act 2026","node_type":"section","chunk_type":"definition","parent_id":"demo-tax-act-2026:chapter:chapter-i","child_ids":["demo-tax-act-2026:subsection:2-1"],"sibling_ids":[],"path_ids":["demo-tax-act-2026:act","demo-tax-act-2026:part:part-i","demo-tax-act-2026:chapter:chapter-i","demo-tax-act-2026:section:2"],"path_labels":["Demo Tax Act 2026","Part I","Chapter I","Section 2"],"part_number":"I","part_title":"PRELIMINARY","chapter_number":"I","chapter_title":"GENERAL PROVISIONS","section